{"type":null,"faqId":40423,"title":"为什么使用路由器后打开网页速度慢，或者很难打开网页，无法收发邮件？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:0.35416666in;margin-top:0.083333336in;margin-bottom:0.090277776in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;color:#00a0e9;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>可能是因为计算机的DNS服务器地址不正确或者WAN接口最大发送单元（MTU）不恰当。您可以按照以下步骤进行排查。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">检查一：确认计算机的DNS服务器地址是否正确</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击桌面右下角的图标</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137240\" style=\"width:0.17916666in;height:0.17847222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，选择“</span><span class=\"s3\">打开网络和共享中心</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137241\" style=\"width:2.7555556in;height:1.3020834in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s3\">更改适配器设置</span><span>”。右键单击本地连接，选择“</span><span class=\"s3\">属性</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137242\" style=\"width:2.7604167in;height:2.6979167in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>双击“ </span><span class=\"s3\">Internet 协议版本4（TCP/IPv4）</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137243\" style=\"width:3.9375in;height:4.7680554in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>确认计算机是否是 “</span><span class=\"s3\">自动获得 DNS 服务器地址</span><span>”或已手动设置了正确的”</span><span class=\"s3\">首选DNS服务器</span><span>”和“</span><span class=\"s3\">备用DNS服务器</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137244\" style=\"width:4.3118057in;height:4.478472in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137245\" style=\"width:0.17847222in;height:0.19722222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>具体的DNS服务器地址可以咨询您的宽带服务商。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">检查二：尝试重新设置WAN接口MTU值</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>MTU即最大传输单元。网络中对传输的数据包大小有限制，路由器的MTU默认值根据国际标准设置，可达到最大效率。但有部分宽带服务商未按照国际标准设置，自行将默认值调小，使得有些比较大的数据包无法通过。因此，可以通过将MTU值调小来快速解决此问题。具体方法如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>登录路由器Web配置界面</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>进入“</span><span class=\"s3\">我要上网</span><span>”页面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>将“</span><span class=\"s3\">最大传输单元（MTU）</span><span>”值由默认的1500或1492修改为1400或更小进行尝试。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137246\" style=\"width:5.508333in;height:5.671528in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5770","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441768486000,"seriesProductName":"WS832-10","visitedTimes":31,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}